<h1>Coastal Euro Summer Fit</h1>
<p>Nothing feels more timeless for vacation season than a white sleeveless knit top styled with breezy linen shorts and leather sandals.</p>
<p>The woven straw tote, beachy accessories, and neutral tones create the ultimate effortless euro summer aesthetic.</p>
<p>It’s an easy warm-weather outfit you’ll want to repeat for beach towns, cafés, and sunset walks all summer long.</p>
