<figure class="post__image post__image--left"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy"  src="https://matchalooks.com/media/posts/6/C1-1-P1-3-2x3-OI6-Sleeveless-Knit.jpg" alt="An American woman is in a chic feminine night-out outfit style wearing a black sleeveless knit top from Amazon—she styles her outfit with a black satin maxi skirt and heeled sandals at a rooftop city restaurant." width="1024" height="1536" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://matchalooks.com/media/posts/6/responsive/C1-1-P1-3-2x3-OI6-Sleeveless-Knit-xs.jpg 300w ,https://matchalooks.com/media/posts/6/responsive/C1-1-P1-3-2x3-OI6-Sleeveless-Knit-sm.jpg 480w ,https://matchalooks.com/media/posts/6/responsive/C1-1-P1-3-2x3-OI6-Sleeveless-Knit-md.jpg 768w ,https://matchalooks.com/media/posts/6/responsive/C1-1-P1-3-2x3-OI6-Sleeveless-Knit-lg.jpg 1024w"></figure>
