            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://matchalooks.com/media/posts/1/C1-1-P1-1-16x9-F6-SC-Square-Neck-Tee.jpg" class="type:primaryImage" alt="A fashion collage featuring six chic American women’s outfits styled with square neck tops from Amazon. Looks include casual jeans and sneakers, office trousers, satin brunch skirts, airport travel pants, euro summer linen shorts, and elegant date-night satin skirts. Clean girl and rich minimal aesthetics with feminine neutral styling in black, cream, beige, denim blue, blush pink, and gold tones." /></p>
                <p>A square neck top is one of those wardrobe basics that instantly makes an outfit look more elevated. It’s flattering, feminine, and easy to style for both casual and dressed-up looks. Here are 6 clean and chic outfit ideas using one versatile Amazon square neck top.</p>
